&lt;p&gt;This is just the general gist.  We’ll put all of this together in a few more paragraphs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;Minify-CSS&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#Minify-CSS&#34; class=&#34;headerlink&#34; title=&#34;Minify CSS&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Minify CSS&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;To minify CSS, I decided to use &lt;a href=&#34;//www.npmjs.com/package/gulp-cssnano&#34;&gt;gulp-cssnano&lt;/a&gt; Install gulp-cssnano using:&lt;/p&gt;
